sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser<br/>(Data Scientist)
    participant Gateway as Gateway API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAuth as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP (Auth)
    participant Fastify as Fastify Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant BFF as BFF Sidecar<br/>(e.g., Gen AI 8143/TCP)
    participant Upstream as Upstream Service<br/>(e.g., LlamaStack)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP (Data)

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Request to Dashboard UI

    Browser->>Gateway: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>TLS (service cert)
    KRBP->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(can user list projects?)
    K8sAuth-->>KRBP: Allowed
    KRBP->>Fastify: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>Headers: x-forwarded-access-token,<br/>x-auth-request-user,<br/>x-auth-request-groups
    Fastify-->>KRBP: Static assets (React SPA)
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: Dashboard HTML/JS/CSS

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Module Federation API Call (e.g., Gen AI)

    Browser->>Gateway: POST /_mf/gen-ai/api/v1/responses<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRBP->>Fastify: Forward with auth headers<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Fastify->>BFF: Proxy (HTTPS/8143)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token passthrough
    BFF->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(BFF middleware auth check)
    K8sAPI-->>BFF: Allowed
    BFF->>Upstream: POST /v1/responses<br/>HTTPS, Bearer Token (forwarded)
    Upstream-->>BFF: AI Response
    BFF-->>Fastify: JSON Response
    Fastify-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: JSON Response

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Kubernetes Watch Stream (WebSocket)

    Browser->>Gateway: Upgrade: websocket<br/>WSS/443
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward WSS/8443
    KRBP->>Fastify: WS /wss/k8s/*<br/>Token in WebSocket subprotocol<br/>(base64url-encoded)
    Fastify->>K8sAPI: Watch request<br/>WSS/6443, User Token
    K8sAPI-->>Fastify: Stream: resource events
    Fastify-->>KRBP: Stream: events
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Stream: events
    Gateway-->>Browser: Stream: real-time updates

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Inter-BFF Communication (Gen AI → MaaS token delegation)

    Browser->>Gateway: POST /_mf/gen-ai/api/v1/tokens/bff<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward
    KRBP->>Fastify: Forward with auth
    Fastify->>BFF: Proxy to Gen AI BFF (8143)
    BFF->>BFF: Inter-BFF call to MaaS BFF<br/>HTTPS/8243 via K8s Service DNS<br/>odh-dashboard.ns.svc.cluster.local:8243
    Note right of BFF: Token delegation:<br/>user token forwarded<br/>to sibling BFF
    BFF-->>Fastify: Delegated token response
    Fastify-->>Browser: Response
